data.description: Welcome Home to Ballantrae's Kirkwall Section, this home has GREAT curb appeal with four-sided brick, front porch and two- car garage. This open floor plan offers a huge island in the kitchen that looks toward the family room with a gas fireplace. Hardwood floors throughout the main living area and crown molding on the first level. The master bedroom has a beautiful wooden trey ceiling, barn doors on master bath and French doors going onto a covered patio. Extra bedroom and full bath downstairs as well. Upstairs offers a huge loft area and 2 bedrooms with a Jack n Jill bath each with their own vanity. Ballantrae offers a pool with lifeguards, 24/7 fitness center, playground. Ballantrae Golf club is open to the public so bring your golf clubs.
